00:31:29.400 --> 00:31:31.740
But with things like the real
time API and some of these

00:31:31.740 --> 00:31:34.850
deeper features, there's still
a huge opportunity for

00:31:34.850 --> 00:31:38.120
applications to build unique,
amazing experiences for people

00:31:38.120 --> 00:31:43.490
who use Google Drive and fully
exploit the platform and build

00:31:43.490 --> 00:31:47.790
apps that are as good, or if not
better than any of the ON

00:31:47.790 --> 00:31:49.230
apps that we've built
ourselves.

00:31:49.230 --> 00:31:52.290
And I think there's a ton of
potential for this and things,

00:31:52.290 --> 00:31:53.540
everything from education--

00:31:56.080 --> 00:31:58.380
