shipping them via FTP.

00:32:16.110 --> 00:32:17.580
There's a huge opportunity.

00:32:17.580 --> 00:32:20.120
And the challenge for you is to
go and build something that

00:32:20.120 --> 00:32:23.940
is the next Google Docs,
or if not bigger.

